    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend Covid-19 grants to businesses registered after 11 March",
        "additional_details": "I purchased a business on 25 of March and was not able to apply for any coronavirus support grants. I worked throughout lockdown and found it extremely difficult to cope, when other business were able to apply for multiple types of funding.\r\n \r\nThe Government should extend Covid-19 grants to businesses registered after 11 March, many of which have suffered due to Covid-19 but have been unable to access Government support.",
        "background": "Businesses registered after 11 of march did not qualify for coronavirus business support grants and many are struggling to cope without support from the Government.",
